title: Dungeons and dragons 3.5 edition book collection v2.0
description: Here is an update to my previous torrent. after 7 months i have obtained a much more complete collection. I still do not feel it is every single 3.5e book, but it is a massive chunk. I know I am most likely missing a few adventures and probably even supplements and cores, so as with the last one, please comment the missing books. I will be seeding this one probably indefinitely. I am also working on another tabletop torrent consisting of various tabletop books as a kind of starter kit, but that is probably months in the works. for now please enjoy this collection of 3.5e D&D books. I also apologize for the naming mechanics as I am very lazy and have not bothered to rename them.
